本工具仅为个人架设的 World Flipper 私服(startpoint-cn 模拟器)提供本地数据修改,
面向游戏保存/学习/单机自娱。工具本身不含任何游戏客户端二进制、美术、音频或数据包。
使用者需自备合法获得的数据包,并对自己的使用负责。请勿用于官方在线服务或商业用途。

This tool only edits data for a self-hosted, private World Flipper server
(the startpoint-cn emulator), for personal preservation/learning/offline use.
It ships NO game client binaries, art, audio, or data packages. Users must
supply their own lawfully-obtained data and are responsible for their use.
Do not use against official online services or for commercial purposes.
